``Baywatch,'' Sophie Marceau, Sara Michelle Gellar, Sarah O'Hare
(see the sandcastle lady in SI '99 swimsuit issue with Heidi Klum),
Sandra Bernhard (not really, just seeing if you're paying attention
this far), Daniela Pestova, Famke Janssen, Shania Twain (as long as
she's not singing), two of the three Dixie Chicks, three of the
