<SLUG> BC-R-KOSOVO-MONTENEGRO-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
USING THE PRESS FOR PROTECTION IN MONTENEGRO 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By ANTHONY DePALMA   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
