<TEXT>
<P>
   Editors, attention editorial page editors:
</P>
<P>
   There will be no Levendosky column this week.
</P>
<P>
   We apologize for the inconvenience.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The New York Times News Service &LR;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
