<HEADLINE>
DISASTERS' NEWS VALUE NOT SOLELY DETERMINED BY NUMBER OF DEATHS 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID FIRESTONE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Between the roar of an Amtrak train crash in March and
the rampage of tornadoes last Monday, there was a terribly quiet
moment in Arkansas last weekend.
</P>
