<SLUG> BC-R-GAMBLING-DOSTOYEVSKY-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COME ON BABY, FYODOR NEEDS NEW SHOES! 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By WALTER GOODMAN   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Among the problems to be addressed or evaded in a coming report
