night might be a comfort to your young child, but could predispose
him or her to short-sightedness in later life. By Henry Gee. 500
words.
</P>
<P>
   B. IN THE FOOTSTEPS OF DINOSAURS There is more to dinosaurs than
fossilized bones. Fossilized footprints provide graphic testament
of dinosaurs as living animals. By Henry Gee. 400 words.
