<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990510.0177 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-10 13:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1024 &Cx1f; tab-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-INTERNET-MUSIC-BIZ-EC     05-10 1009
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-INTERNET-MUSIC-BIZ-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
