brutality of the Serbs' repression _ but not of the kind NATO
intended.
</P>
<P>
   On May 3, for example, NATO claimed its ``most successful'' day
of bombing so far, with attacks on tanks and artillery in Kosovo
and about 40 fixed targets elsewhere in Serbia.
</P>
<P>
   On the same day, an exceptionally brutal round of ethnic
