Jones industrial average was up 26 points, the S&AMP;P is up 3, and the
Nasdaq composite index is up 28. European stocks were also little
changed. In Asia, the Nikkei edged up 0.2 percent, while Hong Kong
stocks rose 1.28 percent. The long bond is at 5.80 percent. By
Kenneth N. Gilpin.
</P>
