<HEADER>
A1108 &Cx1f; taf-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HACKERS-ON-THE-WEB-(N     05-10 0406
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HACKERS-ON-THE-WEB-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HACKERS HAVE FIELD DAY WITH FREE WEB MAIL  
 (FOR RELEASE THE WEEK OF MON., MAY 10, 1999)
</HEADLINE>
   (This article from the London-based science and technology weekly
