<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-10 17:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1412 &Cx1f; tic-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STARGUIDE-MOVIES-AZR &LR;      05-10 1023
