``Rocketship X-M,'' 1950 &QL; 
``Rocky Jones, Space Ranger,'' 1954-55  &QL; 
``Rodan,'' 1956 &QL; 
``Stranger From Venus,'' 1954 &QL; 
``Tarantula,'' 1955 &QL; 
``Target Earth,'' 1954 &QL; 
``Teenagers From Outer Space,'' 1959 &QL; 
``Terror From the Year 5000,'' 1958 &QL; 
``Them!,'' 1954 &QL; 
``The Thing,'' 1951  &QL; 
``This Island Earth,'' 1954 &QL; 
