   I once wanted to become an atheist but I gave up ... they have
no holidays.
</P>
<P>
   Henny Youngman
</P>
<P>
   Look at Jewish history. Unrelieved lamenting would be
intolerable. So, for every ten Jews beating their breasts, God
designated one to be crazy and amuse the breast beaters. By the
time I was five I knew I was that one.
</P>
<P>
