Brooks was in Beijing staying at a hotel close to the US. Embassy
Saturday when protesters surrounded the embassy. Brooks was not
threatened herself, but was shopping across the street from the
embassy when buses full of student protesters pulled up to the
embassy. (Sjostrom, Palm Beach Daily News) WITH PHOTO (mug of
Brooks). MOVED
