Beach, Fla., when recounting what he witnessed last week in one
ethnic Albanian refugee camp. Goldblum and Mark Levy, both vice
presidents of the Jewish Federation of Palm Beach County, returned
Friday from a five-day mercy mission to the Balkans coordinated by
