<P>
   &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; APPLE  &LR; _ Interim Apple CEO Steve Jobs lays out the computer maker's
hardware and software product plans at the annual Worldwide
Developers Conference, a weeklong summit that celebrates all things
Apple. This year's get-together takes place during an usually
