<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-10 20:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1682 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FLEET-BANKBOS-BOS &LR;      05-10 1501
