notion of a just war is a political con.
</P>
<P>
   God help us if our world order is now in the hands of those
whose history books are closed and whose moral values are
conceitedly summed up by the doctrine that whatever Blair thinks
and does is right and whatever anyone else does is ``evil.'' &QL; 
 &UR; ___________________ &LR;  &QC; 
